CRAZY HAIR.

39
00:01:51.835 --> 00:01:53.803
[laughter]

40
00:01:55.529 --> 00:01:58.048
AND NOW I LOOK
LIKE AN ELEPHANT!

41
00:01:58.048 --> 00:01:59.429
[trumpets]

42
