51
00:02:22.349 --> 00:02:25.006
THAT'S BLAZING SPEED!

52
00:02:25.006 --> 00:02:28.872
BUT BLAZING SPEED ONLY WORKS
IF WE GIVE BLAZE THE POWER.

53
00:02:30.460 --> 00:02:32.048
- TO GIVE ME BLAZING SPEED.

54
00:02:32.048 --> 00:02:36.086
I NEED YOU TO SAY.
"LET'S BLAZE!"

55
00:02:36.086 --> 00:02:38.710
