- YEAH!

59
00:02:50.618 --> 00:02:52.172
- WHOO-HOO-HOO!
- WHOO!

60
00:02:52.172 --> 00:02:53.897
- YEAH. WHOO!

61
00:03:00.145 --> 00:03:01.664
[gasps]
LOOK OUT. BLAZE.

62
00:03:01.664 --> 00:03:03.493
FALLING ROCKS.

63
00:03:03.493 --> 00:03:04.874
- YEE--AH!

64
00:03:04.874 --> 00:03:07.497
AH. WHOA!
WHOO-HOO!

65
00:03:07.497 --> 00:03:09.810
both: WHOA!

66
00:03:09.810 --> 00:03:12.502
[horn honking tune]

67
00:03:16.610 --> 00:03:17.852
- CHECK IT OUT. BLAZE.

68
00:03:17.852 --> 00:03:21.028
