69
00:03:24.928 --> 00:03:27.931
- AND. LOOK.
THERE'S THE MONSTER DOME.

70
00:03:27.931 --> 00:03:30.210
WHERE ALL THE BIG RACES HAPPEN.

71
00:03:30.210 --> 00:03:33.005
- COME ON.
LET'S GO CHECK IT OUT.

72
00:03:41.324 --> 00:03:44.154
[cheers and applause]

73
00:03:46.191 --> 00:03:47.330
WHOA.

74
00:03:47.330 --> 00:03:49.953
CHECK OUT THE SIZE
OF THAT RACE TRACK.

75
00:03:49.953 --> 00:03:52.887
- I WISH I COULD RACE
ON A TRACK LIKE THAT.

76
00:03:52.887 --> 00:03:54.717
I WANT TO BE
A MONSTER MACHINE RACER

77
00:03:54.717 --> 00:03:57.098
MORE THAN ANYTHING
IN THE WHOLE WORLD.

78
00:03:57.098 --> 00:04:00.170
- SOMEDAY YOU WILL. BLAZE.
I JUST KNOW IT.

79
00:04:03.760 --> 00:04:06.453
- HELLO. RACING FANS!

80
00:04:06.453 --> 00:04:09.904
CHECK YOUR TIRE PRESSURE
AND BUCKLE YOUR SEATBELTS;

81
00:04:09.904 --> 00:04:14.426
THIS IS GONNA BE
THE BIGGEST RACE EVER!

82
