TO WIN. THE RACERS WILL HAVE
TO JUMP THE HIGHEST JUMPS.

83
00:04:18.706 --> 00:04:20.846
TURN THE TWISTIEST TURNS.

84
00:04:20.846 --> 00:04:23.435
AND LOOP THE BIGGEST LOOPS.

85
00:04:23.435 --> 00:04:28.992
IT'S THE MONSTER MACHINE
WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP!

86
00:04:34.343 --> 00:04:37.415
- THE MONSTER MACHINE
WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP!

87
00:04:37.415 --> 00:04:40.003
