MY NAME IS GABBY.

93
00:04:49.496 --> 00:04:51.394
- HI. GABBY.
I'M BLAZE.

94
00:04:51.394 --> 00:04:52.947
AND THIS IS A.J.

95
00:04:52.947 --> 00:04:55.605
- HEY. WHAT'S THAT
YOU'RE WORKING ON?

96
00:04:55.605 --> 00:04:57.227
- I'M FIXING A SPARK PLUG

97
00:04:57.227 --> 00:04:59.851
FOR ONE OF THE MONSTER MACHINES
IN TODAY'S RACE.

98
00:04:59.851 --> 00:05:03.475
- WHOA. YOU MEAN.
YOU KNOW THE RACERS?

99
00:05:03.475 --> 00:05:05.891
- SURE I DO.
I'M A MECHANIC.

100
00:05:05.891 --> 00:05:08.411
I FIX ALL THE MONSTER MACHINES.

101
00:05:08.411 --> 00:05:11.483
- WOW. THAT'S SO COOL!

102
00:05:11.483 --> 00:05:15.107
- HEY. WOULD YOU TWO LIKE
TO COME MEET SOME OF THE RACERS?

103
00:05:15.107 --> 00:05:18.076
- [gasps]
OH. THAT WOULD BE AWESOME!

104
00:05:18.076 --> 00:05:21.079
- [laughs]
WELL. OKAY. FOLLOW ME.

105
00:05:25.428 --> 00:05:26.947
THERE THEY ARE:

106
00:05:26.947 --> 00:05:29.915
THE FASTEST MONSTER MACHINES
IN THE WHOLE WORLD.

107
00:05:29.915 --> 00:05:32.642
- TIGER CLAWS!

108
00:05:35.300 --> 00:05:36.612
[growls]

109
00:05:36.612 --> 00:05:39.062
- HI. STRIPES.
- HI. GABBY.

110
00:05:39.062 --> 00:05:40.443
- WOW!

111
00:05:40.443 --> 00:05:41.755
CAN YOU BELIEVE IT?

112
00:05:41.755 --> 00:05:43.791
STRIPES IS A TIGER TRUCK.

113
00:05:43.791 --> 00:05:46.863
- YEAH. AND HE'S GREAT
AT CLIMBING.

114
00:05:46.863 --> 00:05:49.866
- HEY. STRIPES.
I FIXED THAT SPARK PLUG FOR YOU.

115
00:05:49.866 --> 00:05:52.352
- GREAT.
BE RIGHT DOWN.

116
00:05:55.113 --> 00:05:57.287
- WELL. THAT OUGHT TO DO IT.

117
00:05:57.287 --> 00:05:58.530
- THANKS. GABBY.

118
00:05:58.530 --> 00:06:01.188
NOW TIME TO GET OUT THERE
FOR THE BIG RACE.

119
00:06:01.188 --> 00:06:02.707
[snarls]

120
00:06:04.571 --> 00:06:06.538
- YEE-HAW!

121
00:06:06.538 --> 00:06:07.953
YIP. YIP. YIP!

122
00:06:07.953 --> 00:06:09.334
- THIS IS STARLA.

123
00:06:09.334 --> 00:06:10.784
SHE'S A COWGIRL TRUCKER.

124
00:06:10.784 --> 00:06:12.130
GO ON. STARLA.

125
00:06:12.130 --> 00:06:14.822
SHOW THEM WHAT YOU CAN DO
WITH THAT LASSO.

126
00:06:14.822 --> 00:06:17.066
- YIP. YIP. YIP. YIP. YIP.
YIPPEE!

127
00:06:17.066 --> 00:06:18.792
ALL RIGHT!
- WOW!

128
00:06:18.792 --> 00:06:20.207
- YOU'RE AMAZING!

129
00:06:20.207 --> 00:06:22.520
- HOO-WHEE.
THANKS. FELLAS.

130
00:06:22.520 --> 00:06:25.212
NOW I BETTER SKEDADDLE.

131
00:06:25.212 --> 00:06:27.007
I GOT TO GET
TO THE STARTING LINE.

132
00:06:27.007 --> 00:06:29.423
- GOOD LUCK. STARLA.

133
00:06:29.423 --> 00:06:31.321
- WHOO!

134
00:06:31.321 --> 00:06:32.840
YEAH!

135
00:06:32.840 --> 00:06:34.773
ALL RIGHT!

136
00:06:34.773 --> 00:06:37.811
- OVER THERE.
THAT'S DARRINGTON.

137
00:06:37.811 --> 00:06:40.745
- WOW. HE MUST REALLY LIKE
DOING TRICKS.

138
00:06:40.745 --> 00:06:44.438
- DARRINGTON?
HE LOVES DOING TRICKS.

139
00:06:44.438 --> 00:06:46.267
- IS SOMEONE LOOKING FOR...

140
00:06:46.267 --> 00:06:48.304
â™ªDARRINGTON â™ª

141
00:06:48.304 --> 00:06:49.478
AHH!

142
00:06:49.478 --> 00:06:51.928
OOH.
[laughs]

143
00:06:51.928 --> 00:06:53.827
WHEW. I'M DIZZY.

144
00:06:53.827 --> 00:06:56.174
[laughter]

145
00:06:56.174 --> 00:06:58.314
- HAVE A GOOD RACE. DARRINGTON!

146
00:06:59.660 --> 00:07:03.388
- THIS AREA HERE IS FOR ZEG.
THE DINOSAUR TRUCK.

147
00:07:03.388 --> 00:07:06.598
- UH. GABBY.
THERE'S NO ONE HERE.

148
00:07:06.598 --> 00:07:08.807
- OH. YOU'RE RIGHT.

149
00:07:08.807 --> 00:07:10.982
- LET'S TRY CALLING TO HIM.

150
00:07:10.982 --> 00:07:13.605
SAY. "ZEG!"

151
00:07:13.605 --> 00:07:15.745
all: ZEG!

152
00:07:15.745 --> 00:07:17.264
- ZEG!

153
00:07:17.264 --> 00:07:18.438
[laughter]

154
00:07:18.438 --> 00:07:20.923
- SILLY ZEG.
YOU BETTER GET MOVING.

155
00:07:20.923 --> 00:07:22.890
IT'S ALMOST TIME FOR THE RACE.

156
00:07:22.890 --> 00:07:24.444
- YIPPEE!

157
00:07:24.444 --> 00:07:27.274
ZEG LOVE RACING.

158
00:07:27.274 --> 00:07:28.344
- WOW.

159
00:07:28.344 --> 00:07:31.140
ALL THOSE RACERS
ARE PRETTY INCREDIBLE.

160
00:07:31.140 --> 00:07:35.040
- YEAH. BUT THERE'S STILL
ONE RACER YOU HAVEN'T SEEN YET.

161
00:07:35.040 --> 00:07:38.009
AND. WELL. HE'S NOT AS NICE
AS THE OTHERS.

162
00:07:38.009 --> 00:07:39.217
[horn honking]

163
00:07:39.217 --> 00:07:42.082
- OUT OF MY WAY!
ME FIRST. ME FIRST!

164
00:07:42.082 --> 00:07:43.946
- HIS NAME IS CRUSHER.

165
00:07:43.946 --> 00:07:46.707
AND HE THINKS
HE'S THE BEST RACER EVER.

166
00:07:46.707 --> 00:07:48.916
THAT GUY WILL DO ANYTHING
TO WIN.

167
00:07:48.916 --> 00:07:50.987
- UH. PARDON ME.
EXCUSE ME. SORRY.

168
00:07:50.987 --> 00:07:53.576
SORRY. I'M WITH HIM.
EXCUSE ME.

169
00:07:53.576 --> 00:07:54.819
- AND THAT'S PICKLE.

170
00:07:54.819 --> 00:07:56.717
HE FOLLOWS CRUSHER EVERYWHERE.

171
00:07:56.717 --> 00:07:58.754
- WAIT FOR ME. CRUSHER!

172
00:08:00.272 --> 00:08:03.552
- HERE WE ARE. PICKLE--
THE CHAMPIONSHIP RACE.

173
00:08:03.552 --> 00:08:06.486
- OH. I CAN'T WAIT TO SEE
WHO'S GONNA WIN.

174
00:08:06.486 --> 00:08:09.350
I MEAN. IT COULD BE STRIPES.
OR--OR MAYBE ZEG.

175
00:08:09.350 --> 00:08:11.525
OR STARLA--
SHE'S PRETTY FAST.

176
00:08:11.525 --> 00:08:14.701
- NO. PICKLE.
I'M GONNA WIN THIS RACE.

177
00:08:14.701 --> 00:08:16.081
ME. ME. ME!

178
00:08:16.081 --> 00:08:17.358
AND YOU KNOW WHY?

179
00:08:17.358 --> 00:08:20.638
- OH! OH! OH!
UM. UM. UM--

180
00:08:20.638 --> 00:08:22.053
UH...

181
00:08:22.053 --> 00:08:23.088
NO.
WHY?

182
00:08:23.088 --> 00:08:25.366
- I'M GONNA WIN BECAUSE...

183
00:08:25.366 --> 00:08:27.437
I'M GONNA CHEAT.

184
00:08:27.437 --> 00:08:28.542
[laughs]

185
00:08:28.542 --> 00:08:29.854
TAKE A LOOK.

186
00:08:29.854 --> 00:08:33.098
I MADE A TROUBLE BUBBLE WAND.

187
00:08:41.797 --> 00:08:42.798
- HEY!

188
00:08:42.798 --> 00:08:44.869
- WHAT IN TARNATION?

189
00:08:44.869 --> 00:08:46.491
- [snarls]

190
00:08:46.491 --> 00:08:49.011
- ZEG FLOATING!

191
00:08:49.011 --> 00:08:50.702
- [laughs]

192
00:08:50.702 --> 00:08:54.637
MY TROUBLE BUBBLES ARE GONNA
CARRY YOU ALL FAR AWAY.

193
00:08:54.637 --> 00:08:57.778
AND THEN I'LL GET TO RACE
ALL BY MYSELF!

194
00:08:57.778 --> 00:08:59.331
[laughs]

195
00:08:59.331 --> 00:09:02.956
all: WHOA!

196
00:09:02.956 --> 00:09:05.406
- WHOA!

197
00:09:05.406 --> 00:09:06.684
- OH. NO!

198
00:09:06.684 --> 00:09:08.513
THE RACERS ARE FLYING AWAY
IN THOSE BUBBLES!

199
00:09:08.513 --> 00:09:10.791
- [gasps]
IT'S CRUSHER--

200
00:09:10.791 --> 00:09:12.931
HE MADE THE BUBBLES.

201
00:09:12.931 --> 00:09:15.555
- COME ON. A.J.
WE HAVE TO DO SOMETHING.

202
00:09:16.728 --> 00:09:18.765
- [laughs]

203
00:09:18.765 --> 00:09:20.594
- HEY. UH. CRUSHER?

204
00:09:20.594 --> 00:09:22.631
ANOTHER TRUCK IS HEADED
THIS WAY.

205
00:09:22.631 --> 00:09:25.150
AND I DON'T THINK
HE LIKES WHAT YOU JUST DID.

206
00:09:25.150 --> 00:09:26.566
- OH. YEAH?

207
00:09:26.566 --> 00:09:28.947
WELL. THEN I'LL JUST GET RID
OF HIM TOO.

208
00:09:34.746 --> 00:09:35.851
- LUG NUTS!

209
00:09:35.851 --> 00:09:37.749
NOW WE'RE TRAPPED IN A BUBBLE.

210
00:09:37.749 --> 00:09:39.095
HANG ON. A.J.

211
00:09:39.095 --> 00:09:40.614
both: WHOA!

212
00:09:40.614 --> 00:09:41.960
- OH. NO!

213
00:09:41.960 --> 00:09:44.342
both: WHOA!

214
00:09:47.897 --> 00:09:49.519
- [gasps]

215
00:09:49.519 --> 00:09:52.005
- WHOA!

216
00:09:57.320 --> 00:09:59.219
HANG ON!

217
00:10:02.118 --> 00:10:04.189
- HEY. LOOK.
THE BUBBLE--

218
00:10:04.189 --> 00:10:05.466
I THINK IT'S ABOUT TO...

219
00:10:05.466 --> 00:10:06.502
pop!

220
00:10:06.502 --> 00:10:07.710
POP!

221
00:10:07.710 --> 00:10:10.644
both: AHH!

222
00:10:10.644 --> 00:10:12.991
- WHOA.

223
00:10:12.991 --> 00:10:14.752
- LOOK OUT. BLAZE!

224
00:10:14.752 --> 00:10:16.823
- [groaning]

225
00:10:16.823 --> 00:10:18.514
WHOA!

226
00:10:18.514 --> 00:10:21.206
WHEW. WHAT A RIDE.

227
00:10:21.206 --> 00:10:23.761
- HEY. BLAZE.
WHERE DO YOU THINK WE ARE?

228
00:10:23.761 --> 00:10:25.314
- I DON'T KNOW. A.J..

229
00:10:25.314 --> 00:10:27.937
BUT WE'RE FAR FROM AXLE CITY.
THAT'S FOR SURE.

230
00:10:27.937 --> 00:10:29.870
- HELLO!

231
00:10:29.870 --> 00:10:32.528
CAN ANYONE HEAR ME?

232
00:10:32.528 --> 00:10:33.702
- [gasps]

233
00:10:33.702 --> 00:10:36.118
THAT SOUNDS LIKE STRIPES.
THE TIGER TRUCK.

234
00:10:36.118 --> 00:10:38.189
BUT I DON'T SEE HIM!

235
00:10:38.189 --> 00:10:40.053
- ME NEITHER.

236
00:10:40.053 --> 00:10:41.951
HELP US LOOK FOR STRIPES.

237
00:10:41.951 --> 00:10:43.988
WHERE IS THE TIGER TRUCK?

238
00:10:48.130 --> 00:10:49.890
YEAH. THERE HE IS!

239
00:10:49.890 --> 00:10:51.271
- STRIPES!

240
00:10:51.271 --> 00:10:53.066
- STRIPES. DOWN HERE!

241
00:10:53.066 --> 00:10:55.068
- BLAZE. A.J..

242
00:10:55.068 --> 00:10:57.657
OH. BOY. AM I GLAD TO SEE YOU--

243
00:10:57.657 --> 00:10:59.589
OOH!

244
00:10:59.589 --> 00:11:01.177
[growls]

245
00:11:01.177 --> 00:11:04.318
