00:22:03.736 --> 00:22:05.324
- [gasps]
LOOK OUT!

487
00:22:05.324 --> 00:22:06.566
GIANT MUD BALLS!

488
00:22:06.566 --> 00:22:07.878
[all groaning]

489
00:22:07.878 --> 00:22:09.431
- OH. NO. OH. NO!

490
00:22:09.431 --> 00:22:12.158
- QUICK. EVERYONE.
HIDE BEHIND THAT HILL!

491
00:22:14.229 --> 00:22:16.749
- WHOA. CHECK OUT
THAT MUDSLINGER.

492
00:22:16.749 --> 00:22:19.614
IT'S HUMUNGOUS.

493
00:22:19.614 --> 00:22:21.098
- CRUSHER MUST HAVE MADE IT

494
00:22:21.098 --> 00:22:23.134
TO KEEP US FROM GETTING
BACK TO THE RACE.

495
00:22:23.134 --> 00:22:24.757
- WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO. BLAZE?

496
00:22:24.757 --> 00:22:26.448
- DON'T WORRY.

497
00:22:26.448 --> 00:22:29.382
A.J. AND I CAN FIGURE OUT
A WAY TO GET PAST A MUDSLINGER.

498
00:22:29.382 --> 00:22:30.418
- HMM.

499
00:22:30.418 --> 00:22:32.454
I BET WE COULD STOP
THOSE MUD BALLS

500
00:22:32.454 --> 00:22:36.251
WITH A REALLY BIG SPRINKLER.

501
00:22:36.251 --> 00:22:37.425
- YEAH!

502
00:22:37.425 --> 00:22:39.875
SPRINKLERS SHOOT OUT WATER
REALLY FAST.

503
00:22:39.875 --> 00:22:41.463
- AND WITH ENOUGH POWER.

504
00:22:41.463 --> 00:22:44.017
THE WATER COULD BLAST AWAY
THE MUD BALLS!

505
00:22:45.605 --> 00:22:48.574
- COME ON. LET'S BUILD ONE.

506
00:22:48.574 --> 00:22:51.818
FIRST. WE NEED A HOSE
FOR THE WATER TO GO THROUGH.

507
00:22:51.818 --> 00:22:54.821
TO BUILD ONE. SAY. "HOSE!"

508
00:22:54.821 --> 00:22:56.858
HOSE!

509
00:22:56.858 --> 00:22:58.411
GREAT!

510
00:22:58.411 --> 00:23:01.241
NOW WE NEED A NOZZLE
THAT SHOOTS THE WATER OUT.

511
00:23:01.241 --> 00:23:03.623
SAY. "NOZZLE!"

512
00:23:03.623 --> 00:23:06.557
NOZZLE!

513
00:23:06.557 --> 00:23:09.457
AND LAST.
WE NEED A SPRING-LOADED ARM.

514
00:23:09.457 --> 00:23:12.045
IT'S WHAT MOVES
THE SPRINKLER AROUND.

515
00:23:12.045 --> 00:23:15.014
SAY. "SPRING-LOADED ARM!"

516
00:23:15.014 --> 00:23:17.534
SPRING-LOADED ARM!

517
00:23:19.052 --> 00:23:20.847
CHECK ME OUT.

518
00:23:20.847 --> 00:23:24.782
I'M A SPRINKLER
MONSTER MACHINE!

519
00:23:26.232 --> 00:23:27.060
- WHOA!

520
00:23:27.060 --> 00:23:28.717
- YOU LOOK AMAZING. BLAZE.

521
00:23:28.717 --> 00:23:30.305
- WOW.

522
00:23:30.305 --> 00:23:31.651
- THANKS. GUYS.

523
00:23:31.651 --> 00:23:35.448
NOW COME ON.
TIME TO BLAST SOME MUD BALLS.

524
00:23:35.448 --> 00:23:38.278
[horn honking tune]

525
00:23:38.278 --> 00:23:39.659
- THERE'S ONE!

526
00:23:39.659 --> 00:23:42.559
- HELP ME BLAST IT
WITH A REALLY POWERFUL SHOT

527
00:23:42.559 --> 00:23:44.043
OF WATER FROM MY SPRINKLER.

528
00:23:44.043 --> 00:23:46.425
SHOUT. "SPRINKLER!"

529
00:23:46.425 --> 00:23:48.530
SPRINKLER!

530
00:23:49.842 --> 00:23:51.153
[laughs]
GOT IT!

531
00:23:51.153 --> 00:23:54.122
- HERE COMES ANOTHER!
- SPRINKLER!

532
00:23:54.122 --> 00:23:56.296
- NICE SHOT. BLAZE!

533
00:23:58.298 --> 00:23:59.714
- SPRINKLER!

534
00:23:59.714 --> 00:24:01.129
- WHOO. YEAH!
- YEAH!

535
00:24:01.129 --> 00:24:03.407
WHOA!
SPRINKLER!

536
00:24:06.134 --> 00:24:08.585
MORE MUD BALLS HEADED THIS WAY.

537
00:24:12.658 --> 00:24:15.523
SPRINKLER!
- WHOO. YEAH!

538
00:24:15.523 --> 00:24:17.456
- SPRINKLER!

539
00:24:19.665 --> 00:24:21.114
- WHOA!

540
00:24:21.114 --> 00:24:23.047
BLAZE. HERE COMES THE BIGGEST
MUD BALL YET!

541
00:24:23.047 --> 00:24:25.153
- QUICK. HELP ME BLAST IT.

542
00:24:25.153 --> 00:24:27.638
SHOUT. "SPRINKLER!"

543
00:24:27.638 --> 00:24:29.329
SPRINKLER!

544
00:24:33.506 --> 00:24:36.129
OH. OH. YEAH!

545
00:24:36.129 --> 00:24:38.753
WE STOPPED THE MUDSLINGER.

546
00:24:38.753 --> 00:24:40.375
- THAT WAS INCREDIBLE.

547
00:24:40.375 --> 00:24:43.378
- THE BEST SPRINKLER-ING
I'VE EVER SEEN.

548
00:24:43.378 --> 00:24:45.829
- THANKS. GUYS.
NOW LET'S GET MOVING.

549
00:24:45.829 --> 00:24:48.797
- YEAH. WE'VE GOT TO GET
YOU BACK IN TIME FOR THE RACE.

550
00:24:48.797 --> 00:24:53.215
- COME ON. LET'S USE
BLAZING SPEED AND GO SUPER FAST.

551
00:24:55.183 --> 00:24:56.978
TO GIVE ME BLAZING SPEED.

552
00:24:56.978 --> 00:25:00.740
SAY. "LET'S BLAZE!"

553
00:25:00.740 --> 00:25:03.398
all: LET'S BLAZE!

554
00:25:04.744 --> 00:25:07.713
- YEAH!
- WHOO-HOO!

555
00:25:07.713 --> 00:25:09.818
- YEAH!
- YEAH!

556
00:25:09.818 --> 00:25:11.510
- CAN YOU BELIEVE IT. FOLKS?

557
00:25:11.510 --> 00:25:13.373
THINGS WERE LOOKING
BAD OUT THERE.

558
00:25:13.373 --> 00:25:15.652
BUT THEN BLAZE
SAVED THE DAY AGAIN.

559
00:25:15.652 --> 00:25:19.828
IS THERE ANYTHING
THIS NEWCOMER CAN'T DO?

560
00:25:19.828 --> 00:25:22.037
- GO. BLAZE. WHOO!

561
00:25:22.037 --> 00:25:25.040
- OH. THIS IS TERRIBLE.

562
00:25:25.040 --> 00:25:28.837
- YEAH. THAT BLAZE GUY
IS ONE TOUGH TRUCK.

563
00:25:28.837 --> 00:25:30.667
- YOU SAID IT.

564
00:25:30.667 --> 00:25:32.531
- [groans]

565
00:25:32.531 --> 00:25:33.980
- [slurping]

566
00:25:33.980 --> 00:25:36.396
CRUSHER. ARE YOU SEEING THIS?

567
00:25:36.396 --> 00:25:39.192
YOUR MUD MACHINE WAS ALL LIKE.
"SPLAT. SPLAT. SPLAT."

568
00:25:39.192 --> 00:25:40.469
BUT THEN BLAZE WAS LIKE.

569
00:25:40.469 --> 00:25:44.439
"SPLAT. SPLAT. WHA-HOO.
KAPOW-EE!"

570
00:25:44.439 --> 00:25:45.854
[slurping]

571
00:25:45.854 --> 00:25:47.960
- OH. NO. NO. NO.

572
00:25:47.960 --> 00:25:49.962
THIS IS TERRIBLE. PICKLE!

573
00:25:49.962 --> 00:25:54.518
EVERYBODY'S CHEERING FOR BLAZE
'CAUSE HE'S SO GREAT.

574
00:25:54.518 --> 00:25:57.141
- WELL. YEAH.
HE DOES SEEM GREAT.

575
00:25:57.141 --> 00:25:58.557
- NO. PICKLE.

576
00:25:58.557 --> 00:26:01.974
THEY'RE SUPPOSED TO BE CHEERING
FOR ME. ME. ME!

577
00:26:01.974 --> 00:26:03.320
crash!

578
00:26:04.701 --> 00:26:05.978
[sighs]

579
00:26:05.978 --> 00:26:07.566
- [slurping]

580
00:26:11.535 --> 00:26:15.125
- WHOA. BLAZE.
CHECK OUT ALL THE SNOW.

581
00:26:15.125 --> 00:26:16.713
- [laughs]

582
00:26:16.713 --> 00:26:19.612
THIS IS GREAT.
COME ON. EVERYONE.

583
00:26:21.890 --> 00:26:24.272
[all cheering. laughing]

584
00:26:31.797 --> 00:26:33.074
- WHOO-HOO!

585
00:26:33.074 --> 00:26:34.662
- YEAH!

586
00:26:34.662 --> 00:26:36.111
- WHOO. YEAH!

587
00:26:36.111 --> 00:26:37.665
ALL RIGHT!

588
00:26:39.943 --> 00:26:42.255
- ZEG!

589
00:26:42.255 --> 00:26:44.292
- HEY. THAT SOUNDS LIKE
OUR FRIEND ZEG.

590
00:26:44.292 --> 00:26:46.915
THE DINOSAUR TRUCK.

591
00:26:46.915 --> 00:26:49.504
- WHERE'S THE DINOSAUR TRUCK?

592
00:26:52.093 --> 00:26:54.992
OH. YEAH.
HE'S STILL IN THAT BUBBLE.

593
00:26:54.992 --> 00:26:57.546
- YOO-HOO. UP HERE!

594
00:26:57.546 --> 00:26:59.721
WHOA!

595
00:27:01.205 --> 00:27:03.863
ZEG HAVE TO GET OUT
OF BUBBLE.

596
00:27:03.863 --> 00:27:05.762
ZEG SMASH BUBBLE.

597
00:27:05.762 --> 00:27:07.867
ZEG!

598
00:27:07.867 --> 00:27:09.006
UH-OH.

599
00:27:09.006 --> 00:27:11.526
[groaning]

600
00:27:13.114 --> 00:27:15.426
- ZEG!

601
00:27:15.426 --> 00:27:16.635
OH. NO!

602
00:27:16.635 --> 00:27:19.741
- HE'S ROLLING AWAY
IN A GIANT SNOWBALL!

603
00:27:19.741 --> 00:27:22.330
- DON'T WORRY. GUYS.
WE'LL CATCH HIM.

604
00:27:23.745 --> 00:27:24.953
- WHOA!

605
00:27:24.953 --> 00:27:27.231
ZEG CAN'T STOP ROLLING!

606
00:27:27.231 --> 00:27:29.302
WHOA. OH. OH. OH!

607
00:27:29.302 --> 00:27:31.684
- WE'RE COMING. ZEG!

608
00:27:31.684 --> 00:27:32.892
- WHOA!

609
00:27:32.892 --> 00:27:34.791
[groaning]

610
00:27:34.791 --> 00:27:38.035
- I NEED YOUR HELP TO STEER ME
SO I CAN FOLLOW HIM.

611
00:27:38.035 --> 00:27:39.692
- HELP ME STEER BLAZE.

612
00:27:39.692 --> 00:27:42.246
PUT YOUR HANDS UP
AND GRAB THE STEERING WHEEL.

613
00:27:42.246 --> 00:27:45.560
THAT'S IT.
GRAB THE STEERING WHEEL.

614
00:27:45.560 --> 00:27:46.734
YEAH!

615
00:27:46.734 --> 00:27:50.599
TURN THE STEERING WHEEL
TO FOLLOW ZEG.

616
00:27:50.599 --> 00:27:52.049
- WHOA!

617
00:27:52.049 --> 00:27:53.602
TURN THE STEERING WHEEL LEFT.

618
00:27:53.602 --> 00:27:55.328
TURN!

619
00:27:55.328 --> 00:27:58.366
- YEAH. GREAT DRIVING!

620
00:27:58.366 --> 00:28:01.369
- WHOA. ZEG STILL ROLLING!

621
00:28:01.369 --> 00:28:03.129
- TURN BLAZE TO THE RIGHT.

622
00:28:03.129 --> 00:28:05.649
TURN RIGHT!

623
00:28:05.649 --> 00:28:08.169
- [groaning]

624
00:28:09.308 --> 00:28:11.586
- KEEP HELPING ME STEER BLAZE.

625
00:28:13.933 --> 00:28:15.245
WHOA!

626
00:28:15.245 --> 00:28:16.487
TURN BLAZE TO THE LEFT.

627
00:28:16.487 --> 00:28:18.662
TURN THE STEERING WHEEL!

628
00:28:18.662 --> 00:28:19.870
- WHOA. WHOA!

629
00:28:19.870 --> 00:28:22.908
- TURN BLAZE TO THE RIGHT.

630
00:28:22.908 --> 00:28:25.531
- GASKETS.

631
00:28:25.531 --> 00:28:27.878
ZEG IS HEADED
RIGHT FOR THAT CLIFF.

632
00:28:27.878 --> 00:28:30.536
- WHOA. THIS BAD!

633
00:28:30.536 --> 00:28:33.539
ZEG!

634
00:28:33.539 --> 00:28:36.266
- WE'VE GOT TO GO SUPER FAST
TO CATCH HIM.

635
00:28:37.543 --> 00:28:40.235
- QUICK. TO GIVE ME
BLAZING SPEED.

636
00:28:40.235 --> 00:28:43.307
SAY. "LET'S BLAZE!"

637
00:28:43.307 --> 00:28:46.483
both: LET'S BLAZE!

638
00:28:47.760 --> 00:28:50.176
- WHOA. WHOA. WHOA!

639
00:28:54.456 --> 00:28:57.011
OH. ZEG SO HAPPY.

640
00:28:57.011 --> 00:28:58.909
BLAZE SAVE ZEG.

641
00:28:58.909 --> 00:29:00.221
- [laughs]

642
00:29:00.221 --> 00:29:02.948
WE'RE JUST GLAD YOU'RE OKAY.
BIG GUY.

643
00:29:02.948 --> 00:29:04.950
- GOOD WORK. BLAZE AND A.J.

644
00:29:04.950 --> 00:29:06.883
- ZEG. YOU'RE ALL RIGHT!

645
00:29:06.883 --> 00:29:08.436
- ZEG SAFE AND SOUND.

646
00:29:08.436 --> 00:29:11.232
- BUT NOW WE'VE GOT TO GET YOU
ALL BACK TO THE MONSTER DOME.

647
00:29:11.232 --> 00:29:14.511
- YEAH. THE CHAMPIONSHIP RACE--
IT'S GONNA START SOON.

648
00:29:14.511 --> 00:29:16.513
- ZEG NOT WANT TO MISS RACE.

649
00:29:16.513 --> 00:29:18.964
- WELL. THEN FOLLOW US.
EVERYONE.

650
00:29:18.964 --> 00:29:20.413
- FULL SPEED AHEAD.

651
00:29:20.413 --> 00:29:22.105
- WHOO-HOO!
- [snarls]

652
00:29:22.105 --> 00:29:23.658
- WHEE-HEE!

653
00:29:29.526 --> 00:29:31.977
- HMM. LOOKS LIKE WE HAVE
TO GO THROUGH THIS CAVE

654
00:29:31.977 --> 00:29:33.392
TO GET BACK TO THE RACE.

655
00:29:33.392 --> 00:29:36.464
- BUT WAIT.
WE CAN'T FIT THROUGH THERE.

656
00:29:36.464 --> 00:29:39.743
- HEY. ZEG. THINK YOU CAN HELP
US GET INSIDE?

657
00:29:39.743 --> 00:29:42.953
- OH. ZEG CAN HELP WITH THAT!

658
00:29:42.953 --> 00:29:44.230
ZEG!

659
00:29:44.230 --> 00:29:45.645
smash!

660
00:29:45.645 --> 00:29:47.095
[laughs]

661
00:29:47.095 --> 00:29:49.097
THAT MORE LIKE IT.

662
00:29:49.097 --> 00:29:50.996
- WHOO!
- OH. YEAH!

663
00:29:50.996 --> 00:29:52.238
- GOOD GOING. ZEG!

664
00:29:52.238 --> 00:29:54.516
- COME ON. EVERYBODY.
THIS WAY!

665
00:30:00.281 --> 00:30:02.904
- [yodeling]

666
00:30:02.904 --> 00:30:06.252
- [gasps]
LISTEN. SOMEONE IS SINGING.

667
00:30:06.252 --> 00:30:08.496
- [indistinct singing]

668
00:30:08.496 --> 00:30:10.049
- I HEAR IT TOO. BLAZE!

669
00:30:10.049 --> 00:30:11.292
[sniffing]

670
00:30:11.292 --> 00:30:14.329
IT SOUNDS LIKE
IT'S COMING FROM...

671
00:30:14.329 --> 00:30:15.814
DOWN THERE!

672
00:30:15.814 --> 00:30:19.058
- IT'S STARLA.
THE COWGIRL TRUCK.

673
00:30:19.058 --> 00:30:20.922
- HEY. STARLA!

674
00:30:20.922 --> 00:30:22.579
UP HERE!

675
00:30:22.579 --> 00:30:23.822
- HUH?

676
00:30:23.822 --> 00:30:26.410
WELL. BUST MY BUMPERS.

677
00:30:26.410 --> 00:30:27.964
I'VE BEEN FOUND!

678
00:30:27.964 --> 00:30:30.000
HEY. HEY. HEY.
Y'ALL GOT TO HELP ME.

679
00:30:30.000 --> 00:30:33.521
I'M DOWN IN THIS HOLE. AND--
AND I CAN'T GET OUT!

680
00:30:33.521 --> 00:30:35.040
- SIT TIGHT. STARLA.

681
00:30:35.040 --> 00:30:36.558
ALL YOUR FRIENDS ARE HERE.

682
00:30:36.558 --> 00:30:39.285
AND WE'LL GET YOU OUT...
SOMEHOW.

683
00:30:39.285 --> 00:30:41.805
- BLAZE. CHECK THIS OUT.

684
00:30:41.805 --> 00:30:43.220
IT'S A PULLEY.

685
00:30:43.220 --> 00:30:44.635
- OH. YEAH.

686
00:30:44.635 --> 00:30:46.534
THE PULLEY HAS A ROPE
THAT GOES THROUGH IT

687
00:30:46.534 --> 00:30:48.191
WITH A BUCKET ON EACH END.

688
00:30:48.191 --> 00:30:51.988
WHEN ONE BUCKET GOES DOWN.
THE OTHER ONE WILL COME UP.

689
00:30:51.988 --> 00:30:55.577
- WE CAN USE THIS
TO GET STARLA OUT OF THE HOLE.

690
00:30:55.577 --> 00:30:59.271
- STARLA.
CLIMB INTO THAT BLUE BUCKET!

691
00:30:59.271 --> 00:31:01.135
- OKEYDOKE!

692
00:31:01.135 --> 00:31:04.517
YEE-HAW!

693
00:31:04.517 --> 00:31:07.451
NOW LET'S FILL THE GREEN BUCKET
WITH HEAVY STUFF.

694
00:31:07.451 --> 00:31:10.834
SO THAT IT GOES DOWN
AND STARLA COMES UP.

695
00:31:10.834 --> 00:31:14.182
- UH. HOW HEAVY
ARE WE TALKIN' ABOUT?

696
00:31:14.182 --> 00:31:15.943
- LET'S FIND OUT.

697
00:31:15.943 --> 00:31:17.703
SWITCHING TO VISOR MODE.

698
00:31:17.703 --> 00:31:21.431
MY VISOR SAYS
THAT STARLA WEIGHS 12.

699
00:31:21.431 --> 00:31:23.812
SO WE NEED TO PUT THINGS
IN THE GREEN BUCKET

700
00:31:23.812 --> 00:31:26.056
UNTIL IT WEIGHS
MORE THAN 12.

701
00:31:26.056 --> 00:31:29.370
- EVERYONE. LOOK FOR HEAVY
THINGS WE CAN PUT IN THE BUCKET.

702
00:31:29.370 --> 00:31:31.924
[all muttering]

703
00:31:31.924 --> 00:31:33.305
- OH. OH!

704
00:31:33.305 --> 00:31:36.135
HOW ABOUT THIS OLD CHAIR?

705
00:31:36.135 --> 00:31:38.551
- LET'S TRY IT.

706
00:31:38.551 --> 00:31:41.485
- THE CHAIR PUT THIS MUCH WEIGHT
IN THE GREEN BUCKET.

707
00:31:41.485 --> 00:31:43.453
WHAT NUMBER IS THAT?

708
00:31:46.249 --> 00:31:48.113
4. YEAH!

709
00:31:48.113 --> 00:31:49.942
- 4 IS LESS THAN 12.

710
00:31:49.942 --> 00:31:52.393
SO THE GREEN BUCKET
ISN'T HEAVY ENOUGH YET.

711
00:31:52.393 --> 00:31:54.119
TO PULL STARLA UP.

712
00:31:54.119 --> 00:31:57.329
WE NEED THE BUCKET
TO WEIGH MORE THAN 12.

713
00:31:58.433 --> 00:32:00.573
- HEY. CHECK OUT THIS BOOK
I FOUND.

714
00:32:00.573 --> 00:32:03.300
[grunts]
IT'S PRETTY HEAVY!

715
00:32:06.165 --> 00:32:07.511
- ALL RIGHT!

716
00:32:07.511 --> 00:32:10.514
THE GREEN BUCKET
USED TO WEIGH 4.

717
00:32:10.514 --> 00:32:12.861
NOW HOW MUCH DOES
THE GREEN BUCKET WEIGH?

718
00:32:15.864 --> 00:32:17.107
7!

719
00:32:17.107 --> 00:32:19.799
- WHAT'S MORE. 7 OR 12?

720
00:32:21.663 --> 00:32:22.768
12!

721
00:32:22.768 --> 00:32:25.253
STARLA'S BUCKET
STILL WEIGHS MORE.

722
00:32:25.253 --> 00:32:27.117
- OH. COME ON. Y'ALL.

723
00:32:27.117 --> 00:32:30.845
YOU JUST GOT TO MAKE THAT
GREEN BUCKET A LITTLE HEAVIER.

724
00:32:32.191 --> 00:32:33.641
- LOOK WHAT ZEG FIND!

725
00:32:33.641 --> 00:32:36.264
BIG CAN OF BEANS!

726
00:32:36.264 --> 00:32:37.576
HUH!

727
00:32:38.957 --> 00:32:41.649
- NOW HOW MUCH DOES
THE GREEN BUCKET WEIGH?

728
00:32:44.341 --> 00:32:46.102
12!

729
00:32:46.102 --> 00:32:48.173
- WHOA!

730
00:32:48.173 --> 00:32:50.106
HEY. Y'ALL. LOOK AT ME.

731
00:32:50.106 --> 00:32:53.040
I'M EVEN WITH THE GREEN BUCKET.

732
00:32:53.040 --> 00:32:56.008
